## Testing & Quality

### Rules
- Manual validation of core functionality.
- Ad-hoc testing during development.
- For critical code, implement specific validations as needed.
- Prioritize rapid development-testing-correction cycles.

### Checklist
- [ ] Core functionality has been manually validated.
- [ ] Basic testing with real data has been performed.
- [ ] Errors found are documented and corrected.
